	<BR>Threshold <INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="threshold" VALUE="[% threshold %]" SIZE="5">
	<INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="op" VALUE="recent_requests">
	<BR><INPUT TYPE="SUBMIT" NAME="none" VALUE="Reload">
	<BR><FONT SIZE="-1">Notes: ID represents a position in the accesslog and time is the time of that id. If you blank the entry it will update to the current max(id) value.</FONT> 
